HEADWORD: Longhand
<hw>Long"hand`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The written
characters used in the common method of writing; -- opposed to
<contr>shorthand</contr>; <as>as, took it down in
<ex>longhand</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

